fset&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;section class=&#34;row td-box td-box--white position-relative td-box--height-auto&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;col-12&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;container text-center td-arrow-down&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;h4 mb-0&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Goldydocs is a sample site using the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/google/docsy&#34;&gt;Docsy&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;Hugo theme that shows what it can do and provides you with a template site&#xA;structure. It’s designed for you to clone and edit as much as you like. See the&#xA;different sections of the documentation and site for more ideas.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
